{"tid":2088071,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港對美出口急跌逾兩成","createTime":"2020-07-01T03:28:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T05:30:57.000Z","uid":25558,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"6a4c0a1cc5d536bb32c53ec6db7b62cb57223c30","tid":2088071,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T03:28:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200630/LK7Z4IGZTQLXJOAUMHCQECOLJQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200630%2FLK7Z4IGZTQLXJOAUMHCQECOLJQ%2F&d=oa%2BbSijZO%2BDWYSsAyiffbuoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=6dd36fd0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200630%2FLK7Z4IGZTQLXJOAUMHCQECOLJQ%2F&h=5677ff50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200630/LK7Z4IGZTQLXJOAUMHCQECOLJQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n港對美出口急跌逾兩成<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/rDmdLj0c5oRxjbq3FLng3nbXJXQ=/190x116/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GE2VAJZ5D3TB3YERHBVU7TS3U4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FrDmdLj0c5oRxjbq3FLng3nbXJXQ%3D%2F190x116%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGE2VAJZ5D3TB3YERHBVU7TS3U4.jpg&h=005bf2d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n統計處公佈上月對外商品貿易數據顯示，商品出口貨值按年跌幅擴大。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】本港貿易情況繼續惡化。政府統計處公佈上月對外商品貿易數據顯示，商品整體出口貨值3,176.1億元，按年降7.4%，較4月的3.7%擴大一倍；商品進口貨值3,313.41億元，較去年同期跌12.3%。由年初起計算，進口及出口分別下降8%及9.8%，至14,573.6億及15,990.61億元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n僅出口內地台灣錄增長<br />\n<br />\n出口方面，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n美國、英國及日本進口則下降18.2%、15.1%、8.7%及4.4%。<br />\n<br />\n貿易金額減少，主要因為通訊、錄音及音響設備和儀器、非金屬礦物製品，以及珠寶、金飾及銀器的交易減少所致；但電動機械、儀器和用具及零件，以及動力產生機械及儀器的貿易增長抵銷了部份降幅。<br />\n<br />\n政府發言人指，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n展望未來，<br />\n。。。。。"},{"pid":"d08928c4e6e20b2909a786133ac7f21aa5308515","tid":2088071,"uid":290883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T03:30:00.000Z","msg":"唔怕，信黨！信國家！"},{"pid":"36fd734bca0935a0986b14c47dc5e7eff231282f","tid":2088071,"uid":57674,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T03:31:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係美國入口減少<br />\n美國佬玩火自焚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e36bfc0031b840cc869d28644d5e0459de414334","tid":2088071,"uid":29093,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T03:32:05.000Z","msg":"美國一定很痛了吧    哈哈哈   !<br />\n<br />\n腥港強大了 !    哈哈哈   !"},{"pid":"d443a4bdc0ec4a33cad6d626ddc2a1136232232f","tid":2088071,"uid":237459,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"36fd734bca0935a0986b14c47dc5e7eff231282f","tid":2088071,"uid":57674,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T03:31:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係美國入口減少<br />\n美國佬玩火自焚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T03:32:46.000Z","msg":"曲到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17021ad3654608d8b4dbb27fbdf50f9ba180cfe4","tid":2088071,"uid":51920,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T03:33:29.000Z","msg":"賺少左2成外匯  <br />\n唔緊要 有港人mpf 全力買中慨股 填數<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47102022c0eb3aa4da9e74df1483ccaca9ef1173","tid":2088071,"uid":250508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36fd734bca0935a0986b14c47dc5e7eff231282f","tid":2088071,"uid":57674,"like":3,